visitor - Variable in class qlang.core.lang.Environment
 
Visitor - Class in qlang.core.lang
All of these methods follow a simple format, essentially the following: visit_____Expression(params) The _____ is always replaced with what the method does Typically, they are self-explanatory, for instance 'visitSelfExpression' is what handles the 'self' keyword The most important class by far: the visitor class.
